reviewText: Nicely covered... Learned she had 2 children with Marc Anthony not mentioned in Hollywood film... Would have been  interesting to know what happened to them... we know he 1st boy with Cesar was killed young... Nice to view if you like history and/or CLEOPATRA....
My husband is a high school history teacher and wanted this dvd to use in the classroom as an addendum to their Egyptian studies. He was very pleased with the quality and content of this dvd.
The video mentioned information I didn't know about Cleopatra. She was a very intelligent woman. After she died, the Romans took her treasure.
